# Hocalwire Labs Assignment

## Overview
This project is a single-page HTML website designed to showcase news articles in a visually appealing layout. The website utilizes HTML and CSS for structure and styling, respectively, and incorporates Font Awesome for icons.

## Features
- Responsive design that adapts to different screen sizes ensuring a seamless experience across devices.
- Integration of Font Awesome icons to enhance the visual appeal and user interface.
- A dedicated news article section with a realistic news studio background image to create an engaging user experience.

## Setup
To get the website running locally on your machine, follow these simple steps:

1. Clone the repository to your local machine.
